2. **懒分配插入** (`lazy_insert_framed_area`):
```rust
pub fn lazy_insert_framed_area(
    &mut self,
    start_va: VirtAddr,
    end_va: VirtAddr,
    permission: MapPermission,
    area_type: MapAreaType,
) {
    self.push_lazily(MapArea::new(
        start_va, end_va, MapType::Framed, permission, area_type,
